Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yamato is running\Nto stop the explosion of Onigashima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I repeat!\NFrom the second floor to all floors!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flame specter that's heading down\Nto the basement continues to descend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CURRENT LOCATION / ARMORY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it keeps descending,\Nit'll reach the armory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll light up the stockpiled explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the Flower Capital,\NMomonosuke keeps making all-out efforts, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it! I know I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Luffy! Just like Luffy, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zoro continues to fight fiercely\Nagainst King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Deep Pride... Stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma! Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a swordsman\Nwho is held back by his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitetsu III!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good. It didn't fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wado Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did a sword of the Land of Wano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...end up in a remote region\Nin the East Blue?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Secret of Enma!\NThe Cursed Sword Entrusted to Zoro"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got all of your three swords now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Slings and Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enma...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A sword from the Land of Wano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A sword from the Land of Wano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "Sunacchi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told not to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just learned it from an old man\Nof the village a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never said it even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An old man of the village?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That old man\Nwho was always on the sea coast...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know his name...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...for so long...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That white sword Wado Ichimonji\Nand Enma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were crafted by the same person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary swordsmith,\NShimotsuki Kozaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,EAST BLUE, 13 YEARS AGO\NISSHIN DOJO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIMOTSUKI VILLAGE (ZORO'S HOMETOWN)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good-luck word\Nto uplift your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... I have no use for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were you a samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the dojo said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence their gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy will come invade soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:46.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OLD MAN OF THE VILLAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, you shitty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, you nasty old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the dojo too boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was beaten by Kuina again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to practice more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're blunt though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can only forge swords like them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use them for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Swords are tools used to cut people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're made to kill people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordsmiths try to craft them\Nas deadly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every sword has a personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's a swordsman's job to tame them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call a dangerous sword\Na "cursed sword"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! That's a fine sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the weak fear it and call it cursed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords are fearsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they yearn so deeply to be deadly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I made when I was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the greatest piece\Nthat I crafted in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sword was very serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that fine sword\Nwhich gives you chills just by holding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave the name of the great king of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great king... of hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enma"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not concede!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are Kaido's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Because I'm a dragon too,\NI can grab them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't push it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can change its direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do it, who will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let it fall on the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big target is easy to hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your luck!\NCatch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out! Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an inconvenience must be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did they get here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yo, yo! You Government's pets!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll discipline myself a bit\Nand bite on my lip!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll show you a thing or two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Check it out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide has turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The name of the village is Shimotsuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess it wasn't a coincidence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the day that old man died,\NI learned...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that he was Kuina's grandfather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you want\Nthis Excellent Grade Sword back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a bamboo sword!\NGive it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Did you know this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma said this village\Nwas founded by a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary swordsmith,\NShimotsuki Kozaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than half a century ago,\Nhe illegally departed from this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That old man was a samurai\Nfrom the Land of Wano?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The swordsmith, Shimotsuki Kozaburo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine swords watch humans closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They choose the swordsman for themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the sword chooses the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you a replacement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword that was handed down to me\Nfrom my late father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma the famed blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You came to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you chose me\Nand you wanted to test me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wado... Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...2001st win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who should be frustrated...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, when girls grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they get weaker than men...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always saying you're going to be\Nthe world's strongest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me a girl can never be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Zoro. You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the world's greatest, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My breasts have even\Nstarted to grow out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had been born a man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be whining like that\Nafter you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair! You're my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy this, girl that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna say that stuff too\Nwhen I beat you someday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You act like none of it is skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're insulting\Nall the hard training I've been doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't say that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, one of us {\i1}will{\i0}\Nbe the world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll compete to see who gets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just made a promise to me yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away, Kuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have... her sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get stronger for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get strong enough\Nthat my name reaches to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be\Nthe world's strongest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords are guileless...\NIt's not doing this with malice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absolutely right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's my power that's lacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that\NOden was fighting with ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though you took away\Nso much of his Haki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he, Enma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Pirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all cut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us take his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we beat him, we'll get promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to control my Haki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll die if I keep releasing\Nthis much Haki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be a king?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight the Navy together now,\Nyou'll be a Government-defying villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer that,\Nor being killed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the devil's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your pirate,\Nif I'm just gonna die here instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look, I have an ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, honor doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's as a criminal or whatever else,\NI will spread my name throughout the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since {\i1}you{\i0} asked me to join your crew,\Nif I wind up having to give my ambition up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better slit your belly\Nand apologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!\NThe world's greatest swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates would need\Nno less than that on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:22:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a promise to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my captain and best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A cyborg that provokes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Queen's attacks remind Sanji of Germa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is a ruthless heart the way to victory?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As he questions himself about the fate\Nhe thought he had broken free of,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an unknown blue flame flares up\Nin his nearly frozen soul!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Strike of an Ifrit! Sanji vs. Queen"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
